WEBVTT

00:01:10.000 --> 00:01:16.000
Ah, it's so hot. It's so hot.

00:01:16.000 --> 00:01:23.000
Ah, so good! On a hot holiday like this, eating snowflake bingsu at home is the best.

00:01:23.000 --> 00:01:33.000
Curling! Sweep! Sweep!

00:01:33.000 --> 00:01:35.000
Yay!

00:01:35.000 --> 00:01:37.000
You guys know how to play curling?

00:01:37.000 --> 00:01:44.000
Of course! It's a traditional summer sport only elegant princesses play!

00:01:44.000 --> 00:01:47.000
Ah!

00:01:47.000 --> 00:01:50.000
Hey, if it's an elegant sport...

00:01:50.000 --> 00:01:53.000
Then you should be elegant!

00:01:53.000 --> 00:02:00.000
Right! Elegance!

00:02:00.000 --> 00:02:02.000
Whatever!

00:02:02.000 --> 00:02:07.000
Ah!

00:02:07.000 --> 00:02:11.000
Yay!

00:02:11.000 --> 00:02:17.000
But the ice melted so quickly, it's not fun!

00:02:17.000 --> 00:02:22.000
When we played this game, Snowping always kept the ice from melting, so it was nice.

00:02:22.000 --> 00:02:24.000
Snowping, you say?

00:02:24.000 --> 00:02:29.000
Yeah! Snowping is the princess of a snow country where it always snows.

00:02:29.000 --> 00:02:34.000
And in the sky of that country, there's a huge snow-making machine!

00:02:34.000 --> 00:02:39.000
And actually, Snowping is...

00:02:39.000 --> 00:02:58.000
Rather than a princess, she's closer to a wild beast?!

00:02:58.000 --> 00:03:02.000
I'll sprinkle snow and cool you down!

00:03:02.000 --> 00:03:17.000
Coldly freezing, Snow Snow!

00:03:17.000 --> 00:03:22.000
The subjects here also like ice and snow very much!

00:03:22.000 --> 00:03:27.000
But... it doesn't snow from the sky here, Snow.

00:03:27.000 --> 00:03:30.000
Did the snow-making machine in this country break down, Snow?

00:03:30.000 --> 00:03:40.000
Then bye! My hot subjects!

00:03:40.000 --> 00:03:45.000
No matter how much you stare, I won't give it to you!

00:03:45.000 --> 00:03:48.000
This bingsu is mine!

00:03:48.000 --> 00:03:51.000
I have no interest in such things!

00:03:51.000 --> 00:03:57.000
Bring the Princesses back at once and return me to my original form!

00:03:57.000 --> 00:04:02.000
You... what is your relationship with that princess named Romi?

00:04:02.000 --> 00:04:06.000
Relationship? I have no...

00:04:06.000 --> 00:04:10.000
She's catching the Princess Teeniepings that fell to Earth one by one...

00:04:10.000 --> 00:04:13.000
...and restoring them to their original forms.

00:04:13.000 --> 00:04:15.000
I don't know yet, but...

00:04:15.000 --> 00:04:19.000
If any evidence comes out that you're involved in this...

00:04:19.000 --> 00:04:23.000
I'll turn you into an even uglier form! Got it!?

00:04:23.000 --> 00:04:28.000
No! The more you do this, the deeper you'll fall into darkness! So...

00:04:28.000 --> 00:04:31.000
Enough!

00:04:31.000 --> 00:04:43.000
If all the Princess Teeniepings find their original forms like this...

00:04:43.000 --> 00:04:45.000
Ah, it's hot!

00:04:45.000 --> 00:04:51.000
Why isn't it snowing here, Snow?

00:04:51.000 --> 00:04:57.000
Snowping! This is all because a bad girl named Romi stole all the snow from this town!

00:04:57.000 --> 00:05:00.000
Hurry and find that greedy girl and teach her a lesson!

00:05:00.000 --> 00:05:03.000
What? Romi?

00:05:03.000 --> 00:05:06.000
Ah! That princess I saw back then!

00:05:06.000 --> 00:05:09.000
So that's why! Wait right there!

00:05:09.000 --> 00:05:17.000
I'll take back the snow! Snow!

00:05:17.000 --> 00:05:19.000
Ah, it's hot!

00:05:19.000 --> 00:05:23.000
Should I make snowflake bingsu for you guys too?

00:05:23.000 --> 00:05:30.000
Good! Give me some!

00:05:30.000 --> 00:05:33.000
That's... the snow-making machine!

00:05:33.000 --> 00:05:35.000
It was here!

00:05:35.000 --> 00:05:41.000
How dare you steal others' things! Hey!

00:05:41.000 --> 00:05:44.000
Coldly freezing, Snow Snow!

00:05:44.000 --> 00:05:51.000
Watch out, Romi!

00:05:51.000 --> 00:06:03.000
The snow-making machine is mine!

00:06:03.000 --> 00:06:18.000
We're sliding!

00:06:18.000 --> 00:06:21.000
What was that suddenly?!

00:06:21.000 --> 00:06:26.000
I will definitely get the Princess Pact back and catch her!

00:06:26.000 --> 00:06:33.000
Let's go, guys!

00:06:33.000 --> 00:06:38.000
How do you make it snow... Snowping!

00:06:38.000 --> 00:06:42.000
Give me back my Princess Pact right now!

00:06:42.000 --> 00:06:46.000
No! Hurry up and tell me how to make it snow, Snow!

00:06:46.000 --> 00:06:49.000
That's not a snow-making machine!

00:06:49.000 --> 00:06:52.000
It's an item to catch Teeniepings like you!

00:06:52.000 --> 00:06:54.000
What? Catch?

00:06:54.000 --> 00:06:58.000
So you were doing only bad things!

00:06:58.000 --> 00:07:00.000
If you don't return it nicely...

00:07:00.000 --> 00:07:03.000
No! I won't get caught, Snow!

00:07:03.000 --> 00:07:06.000
Ah, now is the time!

00:07:06.000 --> 00:07:20.000
Good!

00:07:20.000 --> 00:07:26.000
I'll catch it!

00:07:26.000 --> 00:07:28.000
That won't do!

00:07:28.000 --> 00:07:35.000
Coldly freezing, Snow Snow!

00:07:35.000 --> 00:07:42.000
Come this way, Snow!

00:07:42.000 --> 00:07:48.000
No one on the ice is my match, Snow!

00:07:48.000 --> 00:07:51.000
She's skiing so well... No, she was so good!

00:07:51.000 --> 00:07:54.000
First, I have to stop her from skiing!

00:07:54.000 --> 00:07:57.000
Then, she won't be able to move that much.

00:07:57.000 --> 00:08:00.000
Steal those ski poles! Lightly!

00:08:00.000 --> 00:08:03.000
Oh! What should I do?!

00:08:03.000 --> 00:08:04.000
Wait!

00:08:04.000 --> 00:08:06.000
Wait a minute, Snowping!

00:08:06.000 --> 00:08:08.000
I'll tell you how to make it snow!

00:08:08.000 --> 00:08:11.000
What? You said you didn't know earlier!

00:08:11.000 --> 00:08:16.000
That was... because I didn't know, and she knows!

00:08:16.000 --> 00:08:23.000
Me? Me? I know!?

00:08:23.000 --> 00:08:25.000
Really?

00:08:25.000 --> 00:08:30.000
She won't lie in front of a Princess. Ah!

00:08:30.000 --> 00:08:36.000
Why isn't it coming off?!

00:08:36.000 --> 00:08:39.000
I tightly froze it with ice, Snow!

00:08:39.000 --> 00:08:44.000
So I'm done with you now!

00:08:44.000 --> 00:08:48.000
Now you're just a penguin without a hat!

00:08:48.000 --> 00:08:53.000
You guys lied to me without any elegance, Snow!

00:08:53.000 --> 00:08:57.000
If she is caught nicely, I'll return it! Lightly!

00:08:57.000 --> 00:09:03.000
Hmph, such tricks won't work, Snow!

00:09:03.000 --> 00:09:06.000
Wow! You can snowboard well too!

00:09:06.000 --> 00:09:08.000
It's nothing without that!

00:09:08.000 --> 00:09:13.000
I'm the best princess on the ice, Snow!

00:09:13.000 --> 00:09:14.000
Now!

00:09:14.000 --> 00:09:24.000
Rubber band flick!

00:09:24.000 --> 00:09:28.000
How dare you trip me!

00:09:28.000 --> 00:09:38.000
I won't forgive those who lack elegance, Snow!

00:09:38.000 --> 00:09:41.000
What? Since she doesn't have her hat...

00:09:41.000 --> 00:09:44.000
She isn't any different from us!

00:09:44.000 --> 00:09:50.000
Now! Guys!

00:09:50.000 --> 00:10:05.000
We'll save the Princess Pact!

00:10:05.000 --> 00:10:13.000
Ah! My snow-making machine!

00:10:13.000 --> 00:10:19.000
Feathers! Feathers!

00:10:19.000 --> 00:10:24.000
I caught it! Ah! It won't open!

00:10:24.000 --> 00:10:29.000
It's not over yet! Snow!

00:10:29.000 --> 00:10:31.000
Let go!

00:10:31.000 --> 00:10:33.000
Let go, Snow!

00:10:33.000 --> 00:10:39.000
I absolutely can't let my snow-making machine be taken away, Snow!

00:10:39.000 --> 00:10:44.000
Ah! Snowping! This is Romi's!

00:10:44.000 --> 00:10:47.000
I said it's Romi's!

00:10:47.000 --> 00:10:50.000
Right! This is absolutely...

00:10:50.000 --> 00:10:58.000
This is... so persistent, Snow!

00:10:58.000 --> 00:11:04.000
It would be better to look next to you, lightly!

00:11:04.000 --> 00:11:12.000
Are you trying to trick me? I won't fall for it!

00:11:12.000 --> 00:11:15.000
Transform into a lovely princess!

00:11:15.000 --> 00:11:23.000
Open, Princess Pact!

00:11:23.000 --> 00:11:28.000
Graceping, time to be elegant!

00:11:28.000 --> 00:11:37.000
A heart full of elegance! Princess Plie!

00:11:37.000 --> 00:11:39.000
Here I am, Snowping!

00:11:39.000 --> 00:11:43.000
Piriri Catchling!

00:11:43.000 --> 00:11:46.000
Princess Teenieping, Snowping, Catch!

00:11:46.000 --> 00:11:59.000
Into the Princess Cube!

00:11:59.000 --> 00:12:04.000
I ended up getting caught on the snow, Snow.

00:12:04.000 --> 00:12:10.000
I was a great princess...

00:12:10.000 --> 00:12:15.000
Here, eat this.

00:12:15.000 --> 00:12:16.000
Ah!

00:12:16.000 --> 00:12:21.000
It wasn't a snow-making machine, but a bingsu-making machine!

00:12:21.000 --> 00:12:22.000
I'm sorry for the misunderstanding.